Section Manager Sales Distribution  -
Section Manager Sales Distribution
Responsibilities
Job Responsibilities:To manage and administer the daily sales order to delivery - OTD process (Order taking, settlement, wholesale, retail, and stock process), and generate the reporting.To manage the dealers vehicles order, allocation and distribution to dealers through dealer front end system.To conduct sales funneling & market intelligence.Qualification/Requirements:Education:Minimum of Bachelor degree in Management, Economic or equivalent.Experience:Minimum 3 years experience in sales/logistics/production planning.Specific Knowledge and Skills:Comprehensive knowledge in sales process.Familiar with supply chain management.Excellent English and Indonesian correspondence skills both written and spoken.Computer literate; MS Office (Word, Excel, and PowerPoint); and advance skills of MS Excel.Good communication and managerial skills.
